title: About
content:
VANISHING EGO



Twist and turn, turn and twist,

Cruising along the ocean on a road,

Crashing waves, hanging cliffs,

Moving forward, a sense of lingering -

Gives way to more surprises ahead.


As I wonder the grandiose of nature

Vanishing ego disappears completely in

The twist and turn.


Credits: Ravina Shree
